Maintainer: Vincent Laufer <vincent.a.laufer@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/LauferVA/dgg_rules_somatic
BugReports: https://github.com/LauferVA/dgg_rules_somatic/issues
Description: Functions, tools and utilities for the generation of clinical 
    cancer genome reports with the DGG Variant Interpretation Engine. This R package is an integrated part of 
    the DGG Engine workflow (https://github.com/LauferVA/dgg_rules_somatic), it should thus not be 
    used as a stand-alone package.
